            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s dwelling with man to eternity is there."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He looked for a city, his goal, Lord, we share"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And know that bright city, which Thou dost prepare"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is ever our portion, since willing to be"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just pilgrims with Jesus, our roof a tent tree."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
